{
  "id": "adv_event_2406_02_05",
  "title": "Episode 2 Part 5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ラスベガスではお互いにいろいろ大変でしたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We both had a lot of trouble in Las Vegas…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "まあ……お世話になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… thank you for taking care of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あれから少しだけ英語の勉強始めてみたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I started studying English a little bit after that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3985034942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "本気で海外進出狙うならやっとかなきゃなーって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I figured I had to do it if I was serious about expanding overseas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.5182087262
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "きっとこれから海外の仕事も増えてくるだろうし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure we’ll be getting more jobs overseas…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5182087262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　増えますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right? They will increase‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3683088508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.4791836738
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そのたびにあのガキにからかわれるのもウザいですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s annoying getting teased by that brat every time‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4791836738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "自分で交渉とかもいろいろ出来るようになりたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and I want to be able to negotiate and do various things on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さんも今後、ⅢXが海外進出",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ you should also study a little more so that IIIX can expand overseas",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8779140154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "するためにもう少し勉強しておいて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "in the future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.7029934247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ところでギャラの取り分に関してなんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ regarding the division of the fee…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7029934247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "もう少しこちらの割合増やせませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can’t you increase our share a bit more?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ⅢXが加入したことで星見プロの財源も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hoshimi Pro’s finances must be flourishing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9696602822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "潤ってきたことでしょうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "now that IIIX has joined.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.3867580414
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もう少し還元してくれてもいいと思うんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you could give us a little more back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3867580414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "この機会だから言わせてもらうんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m gonna take this opportunity to say this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.923220857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ケータリングに関しても前々から思ってるとこがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve also had some thoughts about the catering for a while now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.923220857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_kor-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、え、待って、スマホの充電切れそ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ eh‚ wait‚ my phone’s about to die――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ryokan-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.5884082476
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6995692889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8662359556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あくまで契約上の付き合いなのに、わざわざ動画を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a bit strange to go out of your way to make a video and express gratitude",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.2329026222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "撮って感謝を伝えるだなんて、おかしな気もしますが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "when it’s just a business relationship‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.49571338,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ryokan-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.3995692889
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一応、私も参加させていただきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but I participated anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3995692889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "角が立つと面倒ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s troublesome if things get messy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7662359556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ryokan-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.8995692889
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうですね、ラスベガスでライブをした時は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ thank you for taking care of us",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8995692889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "お世話になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "when we had the live in Las Vegas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.5995692889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "海外公演は久々でしたし、いい経験になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It had been a while since we had an overseas performance‚ so it was a good experience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1995692889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "一筋縄ではいかないことも多かったですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although there were a lot of things that weren’t easy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1995692889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ryokan-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.2329026222
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "franとkanaを、貴方に押し付け……いえ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You took fran and kana off my hands… No‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.2329026222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "貴方が見てくれていたおかげで、多少は楽が出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "thanks to you looking after them‚ things have gotten a little easier for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4995692889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お仕事の後に、軽く街を見て回ったんですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I took a quick look around the town after work‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4662359556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ryokan-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.4662359556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "たまには観光もいいものですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and sightseeing isn’t so bad once in a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2662359556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ただ、今日みたいに地方のお仕事ばかりというのも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ having nothing but local jobs like today",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6662359556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk008.m4a",
